caption: Relating to the dietitian licensure compact; authorizing a fee.
summary: This bill establishes the Dietitian Licensure Compact to facilitate interstate practice of dietetics. It allows licensed dietitians to practice across member states through a compact privilege. The bill does not specifically target Chinese immigrants or any other nationality, and would apply equally to all qualified dietitians regardless of national origin. Chinese dietitians with proper US licenses would have the same rights and privileges under this compact as other licensed dietitians.
translation: 该法案建立了营养师执照协议，以促进跨州营养学执业。它允许持证营养师通过协议特权在成员州之间执业。该法案并未特别针对中国移民或任何其他国籍人士，而是平等适用于所有合格的营养师。持有适当美国执照的中国营养师在该协议下将享有与其他持证营养师相同的权利和特权。
